{
  "nodes": [

    {
      "id": "START",
      "type": "start",
      "text": "Good evening. Let's reflect on your day.",
      "next": "A1_Q0"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q0",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When something didn’t go as planned today, what was your first thought?",
      "options": [
        "What could I do differently?",
        "Why does this always happen?",
        "I'll deal with it later",
        "Let me try another approach"
      ],
      "next": "A1_Q1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "How would you describe your day overall?",
      "options": ["Productive", "Stressful", "Mixed", "Frustrating"],
      "next": "A1_D1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_D1",
      "type": "decision",
      "logic": {
        "Productive": "A1_Q2_HIGH",
        "Mixed": "A1_Q2_HIGH",
        "Stressful": "A1_Q2_LOW",
        "Frustrating": "A1_Q2_LOW"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q2_HIGH",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When things went well, what made it happen?",
      "options": [
        "I prepared in advance",
        "I adapted quickly",
        "The team supported me",
        "Things worked out without much input from me"
      ],
      "signal": "axis1:internal",
      "next": "A1_Q3_HIGH"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q3_HIGH",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "What role did you personally play in that success?",
      "options": [
        "I planned it carefully",
        "I made quick adjustments",
        "I supported others effectively",
        "I was just part of the flow"
      ],
      "signal": "axis1:internal",
      "next": "A1_R_INT"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q2_LOW",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When things got difficult, what was your first instinct?",
      "options": [
        "Figure out what I could control",
        "Wait for someone else to fix it",
        "Feel stuck",
        "Push through without a plan"
      ],
      "signal": "axis1:external",
      "next": "A1_Q3_LOW"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_Q3_LOW",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Looking back, where did you still have some choice?",
      "options": [
        "In how I responded",
        "In asking for help",
        "In adjusting my approach",
        "I didn’t think I had any choice"
      ],
      "signal": "axis1:external",
      "next": "A1_R_EXT"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_R_INT",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You noticed your role in how things turned out. That awareness is where real control begins.",
      "next": "BRIDGE_1_2"
    },

    {
      "id": "A1_R_EXT",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "It’s natural to focus on what went wrong around you. But even in those moments, there were choices — small ones that shaped your day.",
      "next": "BRIDGE_1_2"
    },

    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_1_2",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now let's shift from how you handled your day to what you contributed.",
      "next": "A2_Q1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Which moment stands out most from today?",
      "options": [
        "I helped someone with their work",
        "I focused only on my assigned tasks",
        "I felt I deserved more recognition",
        "I supported the team beyond my role"
      ],
      "next": "A2_Q2"
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_Q2",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "In that moment, what mattered more to you?",
      "options": [
        "Helping others succeed",
        "Finishing my own work",
        "Getting recognition",
        "Doing what was required"
      ],
      "next": "A2_D1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_D1",
      "type": "decision",
      "logic": {
        "Helping others succeed": "A2_R_CONTRIB",
        "I supported the team beyond my role": "A2_R_CONTRIB",
        "Finishing my own work": "A2_R_NEUTRAL",
        "Doing what was required": "A2_R_NEUTRAL",
        "Getting recognition": "A2_R_ENTITLE",
        "I felt I deserved more recognition": "A2_R_ENTITLE"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_R_CONTRIB",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You focused on what you could give today. Contribution builds value beyond immediate results.",
      "signal": "axis2:contribution",
      "next": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_R_NEUTRAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You handled your responsibilities well. There may be opportunities to extend your impact further.",
      "signal": "axis2:neutral",
      "next": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },

    {
      "id": "A2_R_ENTITLE",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "It’s natural to want recognition. But shifting focus toward contribution often creates more meaningful outcomes.",
      "signal": "axis2:entitlement",
      "next": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },

    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_2_3",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now let's look beyond yourself — and consider the bigger picture.",
      "next": "A3_Q1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A3_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When thinking about your day, what mattered most?",
      "options": [
        "My tasks and performance",
        "My stress and workload",
        "Team outcomes",
        "Impact on others or customers"
      ],
      "next": "A3_Q2"
    },

    {
      "id": "A3_Q2",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Who was most affected by your actions today?",
      "options": [
        "Mostly me",
        "Me and my team",
        "A specific colleague",
        "Customers or end users"
      ],
      "next": "A3_D1"
    },

    {
      "id": "A3_D1",
      "type": "decision",
      "logic": {
        "My tasks and performance": "A3_R_SELF",
        "My stress and workload": "A3_R_SELF",
        "Mostly me": "A3_R_SELF",
        "Team outcomes": "A3_R_TEAM",
        "Impact on others or customers": "A3_R_TEAM",
        "Me and my team": "A3_R_TEAM",
        "A specific colleague": "A3_R_TEAM",
        "Customers or end users": "A3_R_TEAM"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "A3_R_SELF",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Your focus stayed close to your own experience today. Expanding your perspective can often reduce pressure and increase meaning.",
      "signal": "axis3:self",
      "next": "SUMMARY"
    },

    {
      "id": "A3_R_TEAM",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You considered the broader impact of your work. This outward focus often brings deeper purpose and connection.",
      "signal": "axis3:others",
      "next": "SUMMARY"
    },

    {
      "id": "SUMMARY",
      "type": "summary",
      "text": "Today’s reflection shows how you approached your day — in your control, your contribution, and your perspective. Noticing these patterns is the first step toward changing them.",
      "next": "END"
    },

    {
      "id": "END",
      "type": "end",
      "text": "Good job reflecting today. See you tomorrow."
    }

  ]
}
